OL,3,CAuf wiedersehen pet? University asks
OL,4,Cstaff to stop using Geordie term
OL,6,FThe guide reads: "Language is always
OL,7,Fevolving, and it is important to be
OL,8,Fmindful of any trends. Language can
OL,9,Falso be individualised ` what one
OL,10,Fperson finds acceptable; another may
OL,11,Ffind inappropriate in certain
OL,12,Fcontexts."
OL,14,FUnder the section titled 'Talking
OL,15,Fabout gender', it suggests addressing
OL,16,Fcolleagues by their names, referring
OL,17,Fto groups as "friends of colleagues",
OL,18,Fadding: "Avoid patronising or gendered
OL,19,Fterms, such as girls, pet, or ladies."
