OL,3,CAuf wiedersehen pet? University asks
OL,4,Cstaff to stop using Geordie term
OL,6,FIt also suggests avoiding phrases like
OL,7,F"man up", "grow some balls" or "don't
OL,8,Fbe such a girl".
OL,10,FThe guide continues: "They are
OL,11,Fincredibly sexist phrases which you
OL,12,Fmay hear in conversation.
OL,14,F"When these are used to address men,
OL,15,Fthey also perpetuate the stereotype
OL,16,Fthat men can't be emotional, and
OL,17,Fsimultaneously indicate that men are
OL,18,Fstronger than women."
