OL,3,CAuf wiedersehen pet? University asks
OL,4,Cstaff to stop using Geordie term
OL,6,FDuring a debate on Good Morning
OL,7,FBritain on Tuesday (20 August),
OL,8,Fbroadcaster and author Eleanor Mills
OL,9,Fsaid while she loved "the regionality"
OL,10,Fof terms such as 'pet', the use of
OL,11,Fthem "all about context".
OL,13,FShe told presenters Dean Fletcher and
OL,14,FKate Garraway: "There's a really
OL,15,Fpatronising element to it and of
OL,16,Fcourse it's all about context.
OL,18,F"You wouldn't call you boss 'pet',
OL,19,F'babe', 'sweetie', 'love'.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
