OL,3,CAuf wiedersehen pet? University asks
OL,4,Cstaff to stop using Geordie term
OL,6,F"It's about a power dynamic and I
OL,7,Fthink the reason why a lot of young
OL,8,Fwomen particularly really don't like
OL,9,Fbeing called pet or 'baby' or
OL,10,F'sweetie' or something by a stranger
OL,11,Fis 'cause it feels rather demeaning,
OL,12,Finfantilising and patronising."
OL,14,FFormer big brother contestant Mark
OL,15,FByron disagreed, and told viewers he
OL,16,Fdid not believe terms of endearment
OL,17,Flike 'pet' were sexist.
