OL,3,CAuf wiedersehen pet? University asks
OL,4,Cstaff to stop using Geordie term
OL,6,FHe said: "I think it's sweet. It's
OL,7,Fpart of our regional identity. I'm
OL,8,Ffrom Liverpool but I live in central
OL,9,FLondon which we're really lucky it's
OL,10,Fso multicultural, but you kind of use
OL,11,Fsome of those regional tweaks.
OL,13,F"It needs to be celebrated because it
OL,14,Fis just a term of endearment."
OL,16,FA Newcastle University spokesperson
OL,17,Fsaid the terms were not banned, and
OL,18,Fadded: "Our researchers asked for
OL,19,Fadvice on using inclusive language in
OL,20,Fa professional capacity and the guide
OL,21,Fwas created to help them do that."
